title: Fort McHenry National Monument and Historic Shrine: Museums
body: Explore This Park    Plan Your Visit     Places To Go     Museums              Museums      Star Fort Open  Daily, 8 A.M.-4:45 P.M.  Phone  410/962-4290 Location  Within 200 yards of the Visitor Center. Exhibits  Exhibits of historical and military memorabilia, electric battle map, restored barracks, restored flag pole. New exhibits include the Commander's Quarters, Guard House, Powder Magazine and the Enlisted Men's Quarters. Available Facilities  Restrooms are located in the Star Fort.
